sense.gloss: the year end, end of the year, last days of the year

sdata.j: ↑本日↑↓ほんじつ↓は|↑年↑↓とし↓の↑瀬|↑↓せ↓のお↑忙↑↓いそが↓しい↑中↑↓ちゅう↓お↑集↑↓あつ↓まりいただき、↑誠↑↓まこと↓にありがとうございます。
sdata.e: I am sincerely grateful that everyone has gathered today in this year-end rush time.

sdata.j: もう|↑年↑↓とし↓の↑瀬|↑↓せ↓ですね。
sdata.e: The year is coming to an end.
